      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AMITY ISLAND (2) turned in a moderate effort last time when seventh at this track over 400m behind Jaffa's Monelli (24.81) in a Grade 5. Was a winner prior to that. Form from his last run is proving strong. Should be very hard to beat this time. JUNK YARD LORAIN (8) missed the frame last time out when sixth at this track from Box six (17.66) but draws same box here as latest win. Can figure in the finish. DEFENDER (4) struggled to get involved last start after losing his position early at this track, but prior to that won comfortably by 9 lengths at this track (17.14) beating Just A Madam in a Grade 6 on March 30. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Worth following up. ACE DELUXE (6) has top-three aspirations after placing here over this journey last time.",
